    <h2>SECTION A: Attempt any TWO question.</h2><h3>Question 1</h3>
<div><p><p>Let us consider the 4 bits key set as {1100, 1010, 0000, 1111, 0101, 1001} and input text as {1011, 1110, 1011, 1000}. Now trace the first full round operation of IDEA algorithm.</p</p></div><div><strong>Answer:</strong><br><style>body .mathjax_wrap{width: 100%;overflow-x: scroll;margin-bottom:10px;}</style><p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-59948" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/CamScanner-04-30-2025-12.04n_1-scaled.jpg?resize=1840%2C2560&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1840" height="2560"> <img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-59949" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/CamScanner-04-30-2025-12.04n_2-scaled.jpg?resize=1797%2C2560&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1797" height="2560"></p>
