<td style="width: 50%; text-align: center; height: 24px;">A computer virus is a program that inserts itself into one more files and then performs some action.</td>
<td style="width: 50%; text-align: center; height: 24px;">A computer worm is self replicating program that copies itself from one computer to another.</td>
